(\mathscr H_n,\langle\cdot,\cdot\rangle_n)_{n\in\mathbb N}
\mathscr H
\mathscr H\equiv\bigoplus_{n\in\mathbb N}\mathscr H_n\equiv\left\{(h_n)_{n=1}^{\infty}\,\Bigg|\,h_n\in\mathscr H_n\,\forall n\in\mathbb N,\,\sum_{n\in\mathbb N}\|h_n\|_n^2<\infty\right\}
((h_n)_{n\in\mathbb N},(g_n)_{n\in\mathbb N})\mapsto\sum_{n\in\mathbb N}\langle h_n,g_n\rangle_n.
(h_n)_{n\in\mathbb N}\mapsto\sqrt{\sum_{n\in\mathbb N}\|h_n\|_n^2}
